Taxonomy - Class in hesml.taxonomy.impl
This class implements the ITaxonomy interface which represents an abstract taxonomy based on a half-edge representation as detailed in the paper below.

TaxonomyFactory - Class in hesml.taxonomy.impl
This class implements a set of functions to create an in-memory taxonomy from scratch or from some testing file, as well as other functions to save taxonomy information into a CSV file.
